FBIS4-41426 "drsov122_m_94008" FBIS-SOV-94-122 Daily Report 23 Jun 1994 Tajikistan Gunmen Attempt Armed Infiltration Across Afghan Border Gunmen Attempt Armed Infiltration Across Afghan Border LD2306115194 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service in Russian 1025 GMT 23 Jun 94 LD2306115194 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service Russian BFN [Report by ITAR-TASS correspondent Galina Gridneva] [Text] Dushanbe, 23 June (ITAR-TASS) -- Two attempts at armed infiltration into Tajikistan from Afghanistan by small groups of Tajik gunmen on sections of the Pyanj border detachment, were foiled during the night of 22-23 June by Russian border guards. The Directorate of the Group of Russian Border Guards in Tajikistan told the ITAR-TASS correspondent that artillery strikes were carried out near [border] crossings. It is not known if the infiltrators suffered losses. There were no losses among the Russian servicemen.
